snippet.title: Cassette Beasts - Official Starter Trailer
snippet.description:
Meet Bansheep, Candevil, and more creatures in this latest trailer for Cassette Beasts, an upcoming open-world RPG featuring monster-collecting and turn-based battles. In Cassette Beasts, collect monsters to use during battles, and combine any two monster forms through the game's Fusion System to create unique, powerful new creatures.

#GameTrailers
